{"tid":243354,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"星座撚真係好撚煩","createTime":"2017-05-14T14:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T14:10:11.000Z","uid":28802,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8225f7991638adc4dfe4451e131d772e898ff177","tid":243354,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊永遠有一兩個星座撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野都可以拉到去星座度講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連講正經野都係</span></span><br />\n唔同意你嘅講法就西曬面<br />\n一定搬一大堆野嚟同人理論<br />\n又話雙魚同唔啱咩座<br />\n乜撚野山羊座點點點<br />\n我明每個人都有自己嘅興趣<br />\n真係講親乜都拉星座出嚟講嘅話<br />\n仲煩閪過啲碌柒風水佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5943a1d172dedb0d69eba2602dcc67bf1c9852f9","tid":243354,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864b21aa8fb7245ffb7fddc85b8a2e7f3bd84afa","tid":243354,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6df70e7d70df6800df223f7b37a6788bb72486","tid":243354,"uid":1170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"岩啊"},{"pid":"8df8fd150cd86fac3856f4b81412f0645f4950b4","tid":243354,"uid":47480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:50:32.000Z","msg":"信星座仲廢過廢老"},{"pid":"17f93de90b52e33639967509812c6d6f9ba2612e","tid":243354,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:50:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3368b6e97d8c967a911e479f40656281b750626","tid":243354,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信星座仲廢過廢老</blockquot